title: THE MANDALORIAN Season 2 Episode 1 Breakdown, Theories, and Details You Missed! Is BOBA FETT Back?
author: Think Story
comment:
🏜️ Total DUNE and TREMORS vibes! 🏜️ What did ya'll think of the episode?
Check out my other Mandalorian Breakdowns here: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLY9KJ1cFVs7iB3-JitOOncA-oLH2AD-Tq

My favorite part of The Mandalorian is how it wastes no time getting to the awesome stuff.  I never expected to see Boba Fett in this episode.  I honestly thought we wouldn't see him until episode 3 or 4

The set up first showing the Mandalorian’s ability to survive being eaten by a giant creature was an excellent set up for Boba Fett. It planted a seed in our minds first so we don’t question Boba’s return. The twist is improved by the fake out of giving Marshall Fett’s armor!
I knew boba fett will be in this season but had no idea it would be in the first episode. Amazing episode! I hope boba wears his armour again!!

You can’t skip over the fact that Olyphant is playing the Marshall after his insanely great show Justified, where he played US Marshall Raylan Givens. This episode was fan service for Justified fans.

He even had Raylans Swagger and dialog style.
